### 📅 11 July 2026 — XInclude Attacks

## Lab: Exploiting XInclude to Retrieve Files

### Overview

This lab demonstrates how XML features such as **XInclude** can become an attack vector when user-controlled input is embedded into XML documents processed by the server.

Unlike a classic XXE attack, this scenario does not require control over the entire XML document or the ability to define a custom DTD.

